This project provides a tool to read the SamFS faultlog.bin an reports the active faults. This tool is intended for use as nrpe plugin.

Build

Becasue the header 
pub/mgmt/faults.h
pub/mgmt/error.h
are not content of the current public API you need for build the header files for SamFS from 

$ hg clone http://hg.berlios.de/repos/samqfs 

and the libs of the samfs packages SUNWsamfsr and SUNWsamfsu

build with:
$ ./configure --with-samfs-inc=<path to samfs source include dir>
$ make
$ make install

Be sure that the nagios user can access the fault log! 
One solution is add the nagios user to group sys:

# usermod -G sys nagios

and restart nrpe service
